Dark Sky Paradise is the third studio album by American hip hop recording artist Big Sean. The album is set to be released on February 24, 2015 by GOOD Music and Def Jam Recordings in the United States. The album's recording process took place from 2013 to 2014 at various recording studios, primarily in Los Angeles, and 2015, Dark Sky Paradise pushed back. The album features guest appearances by Drake, Ariana Grande, Kanye West, Chris Brown, Ty Dolla Sign, JhenÃƒÂ© Aiko, Lil Wayne, PARTYNEXTDOOR, John Legend, and E-40. The album's production was primarily handled by Kanye West, along with additional production from DJ Mustard, Mike WiLL Made-It, Vinylz, among others.
